videos.description: RB Jonathan Taylor scores his second touchdown of the game from 29 yards out as Wisconsin goes up on FAU 14-0.

videos.headline: Taylor scores second TD for Wisconsin

videos.description: QB Daniel Parr finds WR DeAndre McNeal wide open down the side line for a 63-yard touchdown to get FAU on the board against Wisconsin.

tracking.trackingName: NCF One-Play (FAU gets on the board with a 63-yard TD) 2017/09/09 ESHEET

videos.headline: FAU gets on the board with a 63-yard TD

videos.description: QB Alex Hornibrook finds TE Troy Fumagalli in the end zone for a 12-yard touchdown to give Wisconsin a 21-7 advantage over Florida Atlantic.

tracking.trackingName: NCF One-Play (Fumagalli catches TD for Badgers) 2017/09/09 ESHEET

videos.headline: Fumagalli catches TD for Badgers

videos.description: RB Jonathan Taylor continues to tear up the Florida Atlantic defense as he records his third touchdown of the game to give Wisconsin a 31-14 lead.
